|-
|复数主格||{{lang|la|fort'''ēs'''}}||{{lang|la|fort'''ēs'''}}||{{lang|la|fort'''''i''a'''}}
|-
|属格||{{lang|la|fort'''''i''um'''}}||{{lang|la|fort'''''i''um'''}}||{{lang|la|fort'''''i''um'''}}
|-
|与格||{{lang|la|fort'''ibus'''}}||{{lang|la|fort'''ibus'''}}||{{lang|la|fort'''ibus'''}}
|-
|宾格||{{lang|la|fort'''ēs'''}}||{{lang|la|fort'''ēs'''}}||{{lang|la|fort'''''i''a'''}}
|-
|夺格||{{lang|la|fort'''ibus'''}}||{{lang|la|fort'''ibus'''}}||{{lang|la|fort'''ibus'''}}
|-
|}


以{{lang|la|audax}}（大胆的）为例，1t-3d-形容词变格如下：

{|class="wikitable"
!1t-3d||阳性||阴性||中性
|-
|单数主格||{{lang|la|audax}}||{{lang|la|audax}}||{{lang|la|audax}}
|-
|属格||{{lang|la|audac'''is'''}}||{{lang|la|audac'''is'''}}||{{lang|la|audac'''is'''}}
|-
|与格||{{lang|la|audac'''ī'''}}||{{lang|la|audac'''ī'''}}||{{lang|la|audac'''ī'''}}
|-
|宾格||{{lang|la|audac'''em'''}}||{{lang|la|audac'''em'''}}||{{lang|la|audax}}
